{"tid":1432953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制團體提11大訴求　包括促立法禁示威蒙面  重啟逃犯條例修訂   23條立法","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:10:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"47174d6c5c8b5bc0705a118354497b5fc96b71d1","tid":1432953,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"包括：<br />\n重啟修例、<br />\n立即展開《基本法》第23條立法程序、制訂「禁止示威蒙面法」、<br />\n徹查外國反華組織資金在港流向、<br />\n確認6月12日為暴動、<br />\n追究所有6月12日及之後違法暴徒刑責、成立獨立調查委員會追查泛民議員有否參與及協助暴亂、<br />\n追究遊行集會申請人有關活動導致公共設施損壞復修費用、<br />\n開發香港電台公眾使用權等<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/mobile/bkn-20190808141529334-0808_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190808%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190808141529334-0808_00822_001.html&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=70c28b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/mobile/bkn-20190808141529334-0808_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2635c54b5fc3d4f55cd0bfb624ec9cca707ee87e","tid":1432953,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"1f585a3484d036f61ef1cd47d73326bb9a17c4e9","tid":1432953,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}